objects.query: SELECT ConversionRate, DecimalPlaces, IsActive, IsCorporate, IsoCode FROM CurrencyType ORDER BY IsoCode ASC
SELECT ArePartialPeriodsAllowed, Name, ProrationPolicyType, RemainderStrategy FROM ProrationPolicy
SELECT Name, Status, PricingTerm, PricingTermUnit, SellingModelType FROM ProductSellingModel ORDER BY Name ASC, SellingModelType ASC
SELECT Code FROM AttributeDefinition ORDER BY Code ASC
SELECT StockKeepingUnit FROM Product2 ORDER BY StockKeepingUnit ASC
SELECT Name, IsActive, IsStandard, CostBookId, ValidFrom, ValidTo, Description FROM Pricebook2
SELECT Name, IsDefault, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo FROM CostBook

SELECT AdjustmentType, CurrencyIsoCode, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo, LowerBound, PriceAdjustmentScheduleId, PricingTerm, PricingTermUnit, Product2Id, ProductSellingModelId, ScheduleType, SellingModelType, TierType, TierValue, UpperBound FROM PriceAdjustmentTier ORDER BY PriceAdjustmentSchedule.Name ASC, Product2.StockKeepingUnit ASC, ProductSellingModel.Name ASC, TierType ASC

SELECT AdjustmentMethod, CurrencyIsoCode, Description, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo, IsActive, Name, Pricebook2Id, ScheduleType FROM PriceAdjustmentSchedule WHERE ContractId = NULL ORDER BY Name ASC, CurrencyIsoCode ASC, Pricebook2.Name ASC
SELECT Name FROM AttributeBasedAdjRule ORDER BY Name ASC

SELECT AttributeBasedAdjRuleId, AttributeDefinitionId, BooleanValue, DateValue, DateTimeValue, DoubleValue, IntegerValue, Operator, ProductId, StringValue FROM AttributeAdjustmentCondition ORDER BY AttributeBasedAdjRule.Name ASC, AttributeDefinition.Code ASC, Product.StockKeepingUnit ASC

SELECT AdjustmentType, AdjustmentValue, AttributeAdjConditionsHash, AttributeBasedAdjRuleId, AttributeCount, CurrencyIsoCode, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo, PriceAdjustmentScheduleId, PricingTerm, PricingTermUnit, ProductId, ProductSellingModelId, ScheduleType, SellingModelType FROM AttributeBasedAdjustment ORDER BY AttributeBasedAdjRule.Name ASC, PriceAdjustmentSchedule.Name ASC, Product.StockKeepingUnit ASC, ProductSellingModel.Name ASC, CurrencyIsoCode DESC

SELECT AdjustmentType, AdjustmentValue, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo, Name, PriceAdjustmentScheduleId, ProductId, ParentProductId, RootBundleId, ProductSellingModelId, ParentProductSellingModelId, PricingTerm, PricingTermUnit, RootProductSellingModelId, ScheduleType, SellingModelType, CurrencyIsoCode FROM BundleBasedAdjustment ORDER BY PriceAdjustmentSchedule.Name ASC, Product.StockKeepingUnit ASC, ProductSellingModel.Name ASC, CurrencyIsoCode DESC

SELECT Name, IsActive, IsDerived, Pricebook2Id, Product2Id, ProductSellingModelId, UnitPrice, CurrencyIsoCode FROM PricebookEntry ORDER BY Product2.StockKeepingUnit ASC, Pricebook2.Name ASC, CurrencyIsoCode DESC, Name ASC, ProductSellingModel.Name ASC

SELECT PricebookId, PricebookEntryId, ProductId, ContributingProductId, ProductSellingModelId, DerivedPricingScope, Formula, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo, PricingSource, CurrencyIsoCode FROM PricebookEntryDerivedPrice ORDER BY Product.StockKeepingUnit ASC, ContributingProduct.StockKeepingUnit ASC, Pricebook.Name ASC, CurrencyIsoCode DESC, Name ASC, ProductSellingModel.Name ASC
SELECT Cost, CostBookId, EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo, ProductId, Description, CurrencyIsoCode FROM CostBookEntry ORDER BY CostBook.Name ASC, CurrencyIsoCode DESC, Name ASC
